83%25B9%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%2590%25AC%25E9%2597%259C-214500328.html&d=wsLpXOxElywvcqXyO2fdBH8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=a4dc346b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E5%98%89%E6%B9%96%E5%91%A8%E6%8C%AB6-%E5%91%8E%E5%83%B9%E5%A4%B1%E8%90%AC%E9%97%9C-214500328.html</a><br />\n<br />\n中原資料顯示，四個主要地區樓價指數中，僅新界西報跌，按周再低約0.48%。該區多個大型屋苑呎價下滑，嘉湖山莊連跌四周，累積跌幅高達14.4%。<br />\n<br />\n據該行資料，嘉湖山莊本月已錄約41宗成交，5宗成交呎價低於1萬元，包括美湖居4座低層D室，實用面積544方呎，售價538.8萬元，呎價9,904元。屋苑近日不乏低價買賣。中原文家輝表示，賞湖居4座高層H室，實用面積550方呎，景觀開揚，減價10萬元後，以560萬元易手，呎價10,182元，較市價低約5%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMark低吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a477819f9cacaec95314cce6f25de4d17e2312ea","tid":1934681,"uid":21903,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"df619732afbc4c6bb3acbdf44b51475175b386fd","tid":1934681,"uid":89861,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5e2f1e6027525be91b16425b06fcbb8745c30bd3","tid":1934681,"uid":21903,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"fffd7d031ef908c1927fb76b7ad980ac9335d8d1","tid":1934681,"uid":235727,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T04:21:41.000Z","msg":"將軍澳係新界西貢區"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T06:53:14.000Z","msg":"住正天晉 將軍澳站出銅鑼灣地鐵30分鐘都唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都唔算近 我無野講"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T07:09:40.000Z","msg":"半個鐘叫近、全香港幾乎冇遠既地方，元朗去尖沙咀4個字，去中環都係30分鐘"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T07:56:23.000Z","msg":"咁咪睇下元朗跌得勁定將軍澳跌得勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef7c98b63b849ef565c740023222fb1558916761","tid":1934681,"uid":21903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d86f3f23669f66937c56a5ed15dc5f78f3b3f4cd","tid":1934681,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"202